# Windows convenience binary built from tools/kato/. Source lives
# in tools/kato/kato.py; each operator builds the binary on their
# own machine via `python tools/kato/build.py`. The POSIX ``kato``
# shell script at the repo root IS committed (it's a 5-line wrapper,
# not a build artifact). Excluding only the .exe and the PyInstaller
# work folder keeps both visible.
/kato.exe
build/kato/

